yGPT</w:t></w:r><w:r><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:hint="eastAsia"/></w:rPr><w:t>模型进行推理、存储结果和生成报告</w:t></w:r><w:hyperlink r:id="rId5" w:anchor=":~:text=%E6%96%B0%E8%B6%8B%E5%8A%BF%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%91"><w:r><w:rPr><w:rStyle w:val="af"/></w:rPr><w:t>[1]</w:t></w:r></w:hyperlink><w:hyperlink r:id="rId6" w:anchor=":~:text=%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%B1%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%B7%A5%E6%8E%A7%E6%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E9%87%87%E9%9B%86%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E5%8E%82%E4%BA%A7%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%9B%E4%BA%91%E5%8C%96%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%C2%AE%20%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%88%99%E6%92%91%E8%B5%B7%E4%BA%86%E8%AF%A5%E4%BA%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%82"><w:r><w:rPr><w:rStyle w:val="af"/></w:rPr><w:t>[2]</w:t></w:r></w:hyperlink><w:r><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:hint="eastAsia"/></w:rPr><w:t>。例如，美的工业视觉平台采用前端摄像头</w:t></w:r><w:r><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:hint="eastAsia"/></w:rPr><w:t>+</w:t></w:r><w:r><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:hint="eastAsia"/></w:rPr><w:t>机器人采集图像，后端由服务器集群处理数据的模式</w:t></w:r><w:hyperlink r:id="rId7" w:anchor=":~:text=%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%B1%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%B7%A5%E6%8E%A7%E6%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E9%87%87%E9%9B%86%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E5%8E%82%E4%BA%A7%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%9B%E4%BA%91%E5%8C%96%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%C2%AE%20%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%88%99%E6%92%91%E8%B5%B7%E4%BA%86%E8%AF%A5%E4%BA%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%82"><w:r><w:rPr><w:rStyle w:val="af"/></w:rPr><w:t>[2]</w:t></w:r></w:hyperlink><w:r><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:hint="eastAsia"/></w:rPr><w:t>；同时也可在边缘部署专用算力（如搭载</w:t></w:r><w:r><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:hint="eastAsia"/></w:rPr><w:t>Intel</w:t></w:r><w:r><w:t xml:space="preserve"> Movidius </w:t></w:r><w:r><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:hint="eastAsia"/></w:rPr><w:t>VPU</w:t></w:r><w:r><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:hint="eastAsia"/></w:rPr><w:t>的智能相机）以加速本地推理、降低延迟</w:t></w:r><w:hyperlink r:id="rId8" w:anchor=":~:text=%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8E%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8C%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E4%B9%9F%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%8A%B6%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E8%BF%91%20%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%8D%E5%BA%94%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9B%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%B4%E6%88%96%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E6%A4%8D%E5%85%A5%E4%BB%A5%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%C2%AE%20Mo